## Use Case Descriptions

### **Authentication & Access**
- **Sign Up**: New user registration with email/password or social providers
- **Sign In**: Existing user login with credentials
- **Social Login**: Authentication via OAuth providers (Google, GitHub, etc.)
- **Reset Password**: Secure password recovery via email
- **2FA Authentication**: Two-factor authentication for enhanced security
- **Session Management**: Secure session handling and token management

### **Public Access**
- **Browse Public Content**: View marketing pages, landing pages
- **View Documentation**: Access comprehensive documentation
- **Explore Features**: Interactive feature demonstrations

### **Authenticated User Actions**
- **Access Dashboard**: Personalized landing page with overview
- **Manage Profile**: Update personal information and preferences
- **Use Core Features**: Access main application functionality
- **Access API**: Programmatic access to application features
- **Manage Settings**: Configure user-specific settings

### **Administrative Functions**
- **Access Admin Panel**: Administrative interface
- **Manage Users**: CRUD operations for user accounts
- **Configure System**: Application-wide settings and configuration
- **Monitor System**: System health, performance, and usage metrics
- **Manage Content**: Content management and moderation

### **Developer Workflows**
- **Development Setup**: Quick start for local development
- **Customize Boilerplate**: Tailor the boilerplate to specific needs
- **Extend Features**: Add new functionality and features
- **Deploy Application**: Deploy to various hosting platforms
- **Run Test Suite**: Execute comprehensive testing

### **Core Application Features**
- **Data Management**: CRUD operations for business data
- **Generate Reports**: Create and export various reports
- **Collaboration Tools**: Real-time collaboration features
- **Third-party Integrations**: Connect with external services
- **Workflow Management**: Business process automation

### **API & Integration**
- **Manage API Keys**: Generate and manage API credentials
- **View API Documentation**: Comprehensive API reference
- **Monitor Rate Limits**: Track API usage and limits
- **Manage Webhooks**: Configure webhook endpoints
- **Use SDKs**: Client libraries for easy integration

## User Personas

### **Unauthenticated User**
- Potential customer or partner exploring the platform
- Needs clear value proposition and easy onboarding

### **Authenticated User**
- Regular user consuming the service
- Needs intuitive interface and reliable features

### **Admin User**
- System administrator or power user
- Needs comprehensive control and oversight tools

### **Developer**
- Developer building on or extending the platform
- Needs robust development tools and documentation

## Technical Architecture Considerations

### **Frontend Architecture**
- **Next.js 14+**: App Router, Server Components, Client Components
- **TypeScript**: Type-safe development with strict mode
- **Tailwind CSS**: Utility-first styling framework
- **State Management**: Zustand/React Query for client state
- **Form Handling**: React Hook Form with Zod validation

### **Authentication & Security**
- **NextAuth.js**: Authentication with multiple providers
- **RBAC**: Role-based access control
- **CSRF Protection**: Cross-site request forgery prevention
- **Rate Limiting**: API rate limiting and abuse prevention
- **Security Headers**: Comprehensive security headers

### **Data & API**
- **API Routes**: Next.js API routes for backend functionality
- **Database**: PostgreSQL with Prisma ORM
- **Caching**: Redis for session and data caching
- **File Storage**: Cloud storage integration (S3, R2)
- **Webhooks**: Event-driven architecture

### **Performance & Scalability**
- **SSR/SSG**: Server-side rendering and static generation
- **Code Splitting**: Automatic and manual code splitting
- **Image Optimization**: Next.js Image component
- **CDN Integration**: Content delivery network
- **Monitoring**: Performance monitoring and alerting

### **Development Experience**
- **Hot Reload**: Fast refresh during development
- **TypeScript**: Full type safety and IntelliSense
- **ESLint/Prettier**: Code quality and formatting
- **Testing**: Vitest + Playwright testing setup
- **Documentation**: Auto-generated API documentation

### **Deployment & DevOps**
- **Container Support**: Docker configuration included
- **CI/CD**: GitHub Actions workflows
- **Environment Management**: Multiple environment support
- **Monitoring**: Application performance monitoring
- **Error Tracking**: Comprehensive error logging

## Boilerplate Customization Points

### **Styling & Branding**
- **Theme System**: Dark/light mode with custom themes
- **Component Library**: Reusable UI components
- **Design Tokens**: Consistent design system
- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first responsive layouts

