- **Analytics**: User behavior and system analytics
- **Notifications**: Email and in-app notifications
- **File Management**: Upload, store, and manage files

### **Integration Points**
- **Payment Processing**: Stripe/Polar integration
- **Email Service**: Email provider integration
- **Search**: Full-text search capabilities
- **Chat/Messaging**: Real-time communication
- **Calendar**: Scheduling and calendar integration

